Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get your moccoletti!\NHow 'bout a moccoletto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.94,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,350)}Act 1:\NAt Journey's End, We Meet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, hello, Marquise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When did you\narrive on Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I made a loop around the inner planets.\NI arrived only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You arrived just in time\Nto catch the end of Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way...\NWho is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My traveling companion,\nas well as my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Viscount Albert de Morcerf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am pleased to make your\nacquaintance, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My... You're the son\nof General Morcerf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:18.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time on Luna?\NI suggest you enjoy yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a city where all your desires can\nbe fulfilled, no matter what they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he styles\nhimself a count.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, Luna's high society has been abuzz\nwith rumors about him this past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are some who say that he's a nouveau riche\nwho made his fortune on the frontier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...or that he's an alien\nfrom outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...or even that he's a monster\Nin human form, or a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That might be going\na little far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:34.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but what\nis he called?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Death is certain,\nits hour uncertain."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't dreaming or\nsomething? Daydreaming or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious. This proves\nthat it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use it to make his acquaintance.\NTo meet the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?\NIt's a huge hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it. You have no idea\Nwho this guy really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:18.30,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Begging monsieur's pardon, but are you\NViscount Morcerf from room 405?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.\NYes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:27.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from my master,\Nthe Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do\nyou think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think\nof what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he want to talk to two\ncomplete strangers like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His note said that he wanted\nto establish friendly relations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with fellow aristocrats who were staying\nin the same hotel, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:53.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.\NYou're such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At least stay and have\ndinner with the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have some doubts about whether\nthis guy is even a real aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Luna, remember?\NHe's almost certainly a con-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:22.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, messieurs. I am called\nthe Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come now,\nthis won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When a man has come all the way to Luna,\nhe simply must try these dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:36.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? We're the only ones\nwho are eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't touched anything\nall through dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you needn't concern\nyourselves about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:49.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just as journeys traveled alone are dull,\ndaily meals eaten alone have no flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:56.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For me, speaking with guests as I am now\nis the greatest feast I could wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:03.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, what did you\nthink of the opera today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking for myself, I don't\Nnormally see operas very often,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:12.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I couldn't help being\ndrawn into the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, Monsieur Albert, are you saying\nthat you have someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...whom you pine away for,\njust as in the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie and I were chosen\nfor each other by our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:32.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in love like the\nmain character of that opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same with everything\nelse in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something that I can\nlose myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will grab my\nheart and never let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:47.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I set out on this journey\nto find that something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to make it\nsound so noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, the goal of this little quest had\nmore to do with what's below your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youth is\na wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:07.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Endless possibilities. Hopes.\NAnd ardent passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, have you ever been\nin love like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of woman\nwas she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:23.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I, too, once had\Nfeelings for a certain woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:30.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As well as dreams of a future\nwith this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:36.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...all of them ended as nothing\nmore than dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:44.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In short, those dreams\nwere only dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:50.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And in those dreams' stead\nstands the man that I have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bertuccio!\NCoffee for our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for the honor\nof your company tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, sir!\NThe honor was ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:12.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to join me for luncheon\non my balcony tomorrow. What say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NWe'd be honored to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your kind offer,\nbut we couldn't possibly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:25.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Luna's public executions\Nare the highlight of Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The festivities reach their peak\nas the blood of heinous criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...washes away\nthe crowd's sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One cannot speak of experiencing Luna's\NCarnival without having seen this spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not so,\NMonsieur Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:41.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.\NYou're exactly right, Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:46.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall await you here\nin this room again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasant dreams\nto both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NYou don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:11.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was cold.\NHis hand was as cold as ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a\ncorpse's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are today's condemned?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One is a man who committed murder\nout of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One is a man who committed murder\nover a love affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:35.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the third is a man who slaughtered\nan entire family to steal their possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:39.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All three are heinous criminals\nwho are beyond forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:45.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it to feed my family!\NI had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:50.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved wife and child,\nplease forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, spare me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!\NStop it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:03.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord Cardinal!\NI didn't murder anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:08.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My rival framed me!\NI'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, undo\nthese chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have to\nbelieve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:18.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're just saying anything\nthat might earn them a reprieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:23.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!\NI didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!\NShut your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of you and\nyour damn whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I killed\nten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Women and children,\NI killed 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?! Live it up,\nyou bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! I wanna see some more\nhappy faces out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:55.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's card is\nmost entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a bit of sport\nwith this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A sideshow to the execution,\nas it were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have here\na single letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:13.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is a letter of pardon that\Nwas given to me by the Cardinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world did you\nget something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:22.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I have but\nthis one letter of pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To make the choice\nan impartial one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:30.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I have written the initials of one of\nthe condemned men on each card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please choose\none of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, it's nothing more\nthan a little game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, shouldn't we hear\nwhat they have to say first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My good Monsieur Franz,\nwe are not judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what we do,\nthey are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:59.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I merely suggest that we make use\nof that fact in order to enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:04.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2}At this moment, we have in our hands the\npower to offer the hand of salvation to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:10.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hesitate to make\Nuse of that power to do good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:16.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it almost feels as if one\Nhas become God, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:24.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're using people's lives\nas a game?! You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.\NAlbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:30.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A game?\NYes, it is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:36.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our own lives are pieces that are toyed with\nas part of someone else's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever seemed\nthat way to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was of the opinion that you and\NI would be friends, Monsieur Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is most disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:58.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You set out on your journey\nin order to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:04.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To find and grab hold of a new you.\NThrough the exertion of your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:07.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Albert,\nlet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!\NYou'll be sorry you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a game.\NIsn't it, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A pardon has been issued\nby the Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The condemned man\nwho is to be pardoned is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocca Briori,\Nalso known as Peppino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do ya\nlike that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!\NThanks oh so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Long live His Excellency\nthe Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert, you have\ndone a good deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Truly a good deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the show\nis beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:18:00.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't look away,\NMonsieur Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill! Kill! Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:37.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back,\NBaptistin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My vengeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is now set in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go to a cafe or something\nto clear our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or how about hitting\nthe red-light district?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I forgot. Sorry about that.\NYou hate that sort of thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's always\nthe casino...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't talk to me\nabout gambling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who was dying\nto see it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then you let the Count\ntalk you into...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!\NI know all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:25.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"I brought this on my own head, and that's\nwhy I'm angry! I'm angry at myself!" Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:29.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're always fussing\nover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my girlfriend?\NAre you my mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the hotel\nto get ready for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:15.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight is the last night of Carnival.\NYou shouldn't be alone on a night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:21.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be alone.\NToday was the worst day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:18.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be\nin such a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:15.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A passing fling on Luna.\NIt was a trap set by bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:18.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moment by moment, the hour\nof death approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:19.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 2:,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.63,count fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,350)}Act 2:\NUntil the Sun Rises Over the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:21.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 2:,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:22.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."Until the Sun\NRises Over the Moon".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:23.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."Until the Sun\NRises Over the Moon".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:25.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
